---
title: Hoisin Chicken, Tofu & Veggie Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Behind every great stir-fry, there's got to be a great sauce! This one has hoisin, brown sugar and soy sauce – it's a knockout. Toss it through tofu and a medley of veggies for a fast and easy weeknight winner.

